Description: Provides visual tools for preliminary data-quality diagnosis,
    including advanced missing-data diagnostics, correlation diagnostics,
    numerical distribution assessment, and actionable data-quality reporting.
    This package is an attributed derivative work of the 'visdat' package
    developed by its original contributors
    (<https://github.com/ropensci/visdat>). The package extends the original
    visual data-exploration concepts with additional statistical diagnostics
    and preprocessing recommendations.
